---
description: Regras de testes — suite obrigatória, não alterar testes
globs: **/*.test.* **/*.spec.* **/test/** **/tests/** jest.config.* vitest.config.*
alwaysApply: false
---

# Testing

- Run the full test suite after every implementation change.
- If a test fails: do NOT change the test. Fix the implementation.
- Never skip or disable a failing test to make the pipeline green.
